Author: whydiepizzapie
Text: Yeah I think I need to just make myself eat when my fasting timer goes off to start.  I might also bargain myself into a more intermittent fasting type deal to try and make sure in eating at least once a day.

Author: pixelandnasal
Text: I ate so much/regularly over xmas and new years’ time that my sense of hunger kinda came back lol,, so if you want to get out of your train of thought perhaps try eating more regularly (at least once a day) and/or eating bigger meals? I know that can be easier said than done though❣️
